FT  08 JUL 92 / UK Company News: Securiguard ahead 20%
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
HELPED BY a substantial cut in interest charges, Securiguard Group raised
interim pre-tax profits by 20 per cent.
Turnover in the 28 weeks to May 17 moved up to Pounds 88.8m (Pounds 84.9m)
