<TEXT>
TT GROUP, the acquisitive industrial holding company, has made its third
proposal so far this year by taking a 6.35 per cent stake in AB Electronic
Products, a loss-making components maker, and suggesting a merger.
AB Electronic said it was 'seeking clarification' of TT's intentions and
would make a further announcement 'in due course'.
